  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img.wdjimg.com/mms/icon/v1/b/7a/1b7ac6f8826971800db4c448dc1637ab_256_256.png\" /></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p766041\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\tActor Russell Crowe shot to fame 15 years ago when he played Maximus in the hit film Gladiator. Now he's turned his hand to directing, making his <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/debut\" target=\"_blank\">debut</a> with The Water Diviner, in which he also plays the lead. It tells the story of an Australian father Joshua who goes in search of his three sons who were fighting in the First World War and who haven't returned home after the Battle of Gallipoli against the Turkish army. Australia and New Zealand suffered huge losses in that <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/battle\" target=\"_blank\">battle</a> and it's still a very <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/emotive\" target=\"_blank\">emotive</a> subject there. The BBC's Samira Ahmed asked Russell Crowe why he decided to make this film.</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\tFor 100 years since Gallipoli, we've had a very myopic <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/perspective\" target=\"_blank\">perspective</a>, you know. As reading the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/script\" target=\"_blank\">script</a> for the first time, I was simultaneously, really excited and embarrassed. It was like my whole life. As a young Australian born in New Zealand, I've gone to dawn services on the April 25th, Anzac day. If I'm in Australia, I'll, you know, go wherever to Sydney.&nbsp;</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著